Requirements: Android 2.1+
Overview: German male voice for SVOX Classic Text-to-Speech Engine.
Did you know that your mobile can speak German?

Have Markus read aloud texts from your e-book, navigation, translation and other apps in an German male, high quality and natural-sounding voice powered by SVOX.

When combined with TTS-enabled apps, Markus can:
- give directions, allowing you to keep your eyes on the road while you're driving
- read a notification containing the caller / sender's name, and read the content of an incoming call / sms / mms / email
- read aloud your favorite e-books or pdf documents
- help you learn German by reading aloud the correct pronunciation
